<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Reset Password SI PAK-E</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f8fafc;
      color: #1e293b;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }
    .wrapper {
      width: 100%;
      table-layout: fixed;
      background-color: #f8fafc;
      padding: 40px 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 500px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05), 0 2px 4px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }
    .logo {
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 22px;
      color: #2563eb;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      text-align: center;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #0f172a;
      margin-top: 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #475569;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .code-container {
      background-color: #fef2f2;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 24px;
      margin: 30px 0;
      text-align: center;
      border: 1px dashed #fca5a5;
    }
    .code {
      font-family: 'Monaco', 'Consolas', monospace;
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #dc2626;
      letter-spacing: 6px;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .warning {
      background-color: #fffbeb;
      border: 1px solid #fde68a;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .warning p {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #92400e;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer-text {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #94a3b8;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .expire-note {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #64748b;
      margin-top: 16px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="logo">SI PAK-E <span style="color: #64748b; font-weight: 400;">| Reset Password</span></div>
      
      <h1>Permintaan Reset Password</h1>
      
      <p>Halo <strong>{{name}}</strong>,<br>
      Kami menerima permintaan untuk mereset password akun Anda. Gunakan kode OTP di bawah ini untuk mengatur ulang password Anda.</p>
      
      <div class="code-container">
        <div class="code">{{code}}</div>
      </div>
      
      <p class="expire-note">Kode ini berlaku selama <strong>1 jam</strong>. <br>Jangan membagikan kode ini kepada siapapun untuk menjaga keamanan akun Anda.</p>
      
      <div class="warning">
        <p>⚠️ Jika Anda tidak meminta reset password, abaikan email ini. Akun Anda tetap aman.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="footer">
        <p class="footer-text">
          <strong>Sistem Pakar Diagnostik BMW E36</strong><br>
          © 2026 SI PAK-E. Purwokerto, Indonesia.<br>
          <em>Pesan ini dikirim secara otomatis, mohon tidak membalas email ini.</em>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
